                <p class="text-left"> — 挂历？那是上个世纪的产物好吗？</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <img src="http://ongoo1pyy.bkt.clouddn.com/jd-store-lunbo3.jpg" alt="Los Angeles">
              <div class="carousel-caption">
                <h2>展架里摆上的不该是廉价的摆设<br>
